OL,3,GUK long range forecast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Mon 25 May to Wed 3 Jun
OL,6,FWarm and dry for most on Bank Holiday
OL,7,FMonday. Through the week, high
OL,8,Fpressure is expected to remain in
OL,9,Fplace for much of the UK, meaning fine
OL,10,Fweather likely to continue for most
OL,11,Fplaces. Some patchy rain may affect
OL,12,Fthe far north at times and perhaps a
OL,13,Ffew showers in the far south.
OL,14,FTemperatures are expected to be above
OL,15,Fnormal, feeling very warm at times
OL,16,Fwith light winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
